text: Joseph Walcott Parry is a Saint Kitts and Nevis politician. He was President of Nevis Cricket association and a representative on the Leeward Islands Cricket Association. He was the Premier of Nevis from 2006 until 2013. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Premiers of Nevis Category:1948 births Category:University of the West Indies alumni
title: Joseph Parry (politician)
